<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ht">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sèvis ArmrData | Securing your dataworld</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Poppins:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --ble-nwit: #0B192C;     
            --ve-flash: #00D26A;     
            --gris-steel: #E2E8F0;   
            --blan: #FFFFFF;
            --nwa-kad: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--ble-nwit);
            color: var(--gris-steel);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            color: var(--blan);
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px 5%;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.1);
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--blan);
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        .logo-text span {
            color: var(--ve-flash);
        }

        .brand-logo-img {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        /* Hero section pour les services */
        .services-hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px 40px;
        }

        .services-hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .services-hero p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #A0AEC0;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Grille des services */
        .services-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto 60px;
            padding: 0 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .service-card {
            background-color: var(--nwa-kad);
            border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.05);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
            transition: transform 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: var(--ve-flash);
        }

        .service-icon {
            font-size: 2.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--ve-flash);
        }

        .service-card h2 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .service-card p {
            color: #A0AEC0;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .btn-service {
            display: inline-block;
            border: 1px solid var(--ve-flash);
            color: var(--ve-flash);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-service:hover {
            background-color: var(--ve-flash);
            color: var(--ble-nwit);
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.05);
            color: #718096;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo-container">
            <div class="logo-text">Armr<span>Data</span></div>
        </div>
        <img src="logo.jpg" alt="ArmrData Logo" class="brand-logo-img">
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="services-hero">
            <h1>Sèvis Sekirite ArmrData</h1>
            <p>Nou pa sèlman ba ou konsèy, nou blende espas dijital ou pou ou menm ak biznis ou ka travay san tèt chaje.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="services-container">
            
            <div class="service-card">
                <div>
                    <div class="service-icon">🛡️</div>
                    <h2>Blendaj Aparèy ak Kont Pèsonèl</h2>
                    <p>Nou konfigire sekirite telefòn ak laptop ou. Nou aktive sekirite De Faktè (2FA) sou imel, WhatsApp, ak rezo sosyal ou yo pou anpeche pirat vòlè idantite w.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="btn-service">Sekirize Kont Mwen</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div>
                    <div class="service-icon">🌐</div>
                    <h2>Sekirite & Netwayaj Sit WordPress</h2>
                    <p>Nou blende sit WordPress ou a kont atak fòs brit epi nou fèmen tout fay sekirite yo. Si sit la te deja pirate, nou netwaye fo kòd yo epi nou remete l an liy.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="btn-service">Blende Sit Mwen</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div>
                    <div class="service-icon">🚨</div>
                    <h2>Odit & Plan Ijans pou Ti Biznis</h2>
                    <p>Nou fè yon analiz konplè sou fason ou sere done kliyan ou yo ak fason ou fè sovgad (backup). Nou ba ou yon rapò klè ak yon plan aksyon pou evite pèdi lajan.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="btn-service">Mande yon Odit</a>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div>
                    <div class="service-icon">🎓</div>
                    <h2>Fòmasyon Kont Pèlen Pirat (Phishing)</h2>
                    <p>Nou bay anplwaye ou yo ti fòmasyon pratik tou kout pou yo aprann detekte fo imel, fo lyen WhatsApp, ak mesaj pèlen pirat yo voye pou vòlè kòd aksè nou yo.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="btn-service">Mande yon Fòmasyon</a>
            </div>

        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 ArmrData. Tout dwa rezève. | Securing your dataworld.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
